sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_K1675006
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: JIAQI XU
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: Construct the JBA (J23119+B0034+NhaA), B0034 and NhaB with the vector pSB1C3. Two functional genes NhaA and NhaB are used to pump in protons and lower the pH of bacteria???s microenvironment. JBA and JBB are linked with pSB1C3 through 3A Assemble successfully. Thus, it can be an alkaline-resisting part.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableNotes: This is a composite part including the J23119 promoter ecoded in part BBa_J23119 and the ribosome binding site B0034 ecoded in part BBa_B0034. The functional genes NhaA and NhaB are cloned from Escherichia coli str. K-12 substr. sequence found through Genbank http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/nuccore/NC_000913.3?report=genbank&from=17489&to=18655 http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/nuccore/NC_000913.3?report=genbank&from=1233176&to=1234717&strand=true
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableProvenance: The sequence of promoter J23119 is found through the standard part BBa_J23119 http://parts.igem.org/Part:BBa_J23119 The sequence of ribosome binding site B0034 is found through the standard part BBa_B0034 http://parts.igem.org/Part:BBa_B0034 The sequence of gene NhaA is found through Genbank http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/nuccore/NC_000913.3?report=genbank&from=17489&to=18655 The sequence of gene NhaB is found through Genbank http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/nuccore/NC_000913.3?report=genbank&from=1233176&to=1234717&strand=true

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: LacY
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:description: LacY transporter protein from E. coli
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Francesca Ceroni
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: This part has been derived from the BBa_J22101 part. The BBa_J22101 part was not working due to an insertion of 35 bp upstream the LacY coding sequence. We amplified the right gene sequence by PCR and put it into a standard plasmid.

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_K1675015
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: JIAQI XU
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: Construct the JBA (J23119+B0034), B0034 and nhaB with the vector pSB1C3. Two functional genes nhaA and nhaB are used to pump H+ in and lower the pH of bacteria???s microenvironment. JBA and JBB are linked with pSB1C3 through 3A Assemble successfully. Thus, it can be an alkaline-resisting part.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableNotes: mutation of CTG to CTA Leu.(site:1552bp); mutation of GCT to GCG Ala.(site:1630bp); mutation of ACC to ACT Thr.(site:1780bp); mutation of GAC to GAT Asp.(site:1786bp); mutation of ACC to ACT Thr.(site:1891bp); mutation of GTA to GTG Val.(site:1906bp); mutation of GCA to GCG Ala.(site:2254bp); mutation of GAG to GAA Glu.(site:2281bp); mutation of GTC to GTA Val.(site:2713bp)
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableProvenance: The gene NhaA and NhaB come from Escherichia coli str. K-12. The J23119 promoter and the B0034 RBS come from the standard parts.

sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableProvenance: The Lac Y gene has been PCR amplified from the chromosomal DNA of MG1655 (Escherechia coli)and has been inserted into plasmid pSB1A2( Part number BBa_B0015).
